config LUMIA_RIL
    tristate "Microsoft Lumia RIL Support"
    depends on ARCH_MSM8994
    help
      This enables support for the Radio Interface Layer (RIL) on
      Microsoft Lumia devices with MSM8994 chipset.

config LUMIA_CELLMUX
    tristate "Microsoft Lumia Cell Multiplexer"
    depends on LUMIA_RIL
    help
      This enables support for the cellular multiplexer driver
      on Microsoft Lumia devices.

config LUMIA_CELL_USERMODE
    tristate "Microsoft Lumia Cell User Mode Interface"
    depends on LUMIA_RIL
    help
      This enables support for the cellular user mode interface
      on Microsoft Lumia devices.

config LUMIA_CELL_NETMON
    tristate "Microsoft Lumia Cell Network Monitor"
    depends on LUMIA_RIL
    help
      This enables support for the cellular network monitoring
      on Microsoft Lumia devices. 